{"tid":207137,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)死亡筆記2016 明日世界","createTime":"2017-04-18T19:02:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T22:10:40.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e50b289462daebc526feb51cd6ba63cfc9e483d2","tid":207137,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T19:02:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wix.com/thanksyour\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wix.com%2Fthanksyour&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w3adZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=9a4eed52\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wix.com/thanksyour</a> 得返V台睇 CC執柒左<br />\n<a href=\"http://thankyour.kissr.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthankyour.kissr.com%2F&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w3adZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=fead138b\" target=\"_blank\">http://thankyour.kissr.com/</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.ak.crunchyroll.com/i/spire3/89692d04ce4791acded7eab88ea91d771472083544_full.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.ak.crunchyroll.com%2Fi%2Fspire3%2F89692d04ce4791acded7eab88ea91d771472083544_full.jpg&h=a1c29fb4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/80/Tomorrowland_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F80%2FTomorrowland_poster.jpg&h=30c18a5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.根據官方釋出的情報，故事將以至今電影、電視劇、動畫、舞台劇、都未曾出現，以原作存在的死亡筆記本「6本規則」為基礎展開。6 本規則為「人間界同時存在的筆記本最多6本。死神自己所持有的筆記不算在內。另外以將筆記讓人類所有為由，能滯留在人間界死神也最多6隻」。故事將圍繞著掉落於地面的6本死亡筆記本所引起的爭奪戰鬥展開 (你只要集齊全部筆記就可以召喚神龍)<br />\n<br />\n2.十九世紀末，愛迪生、巴黎鐵塔設計師艾菲爾、交流電之父特斯拉、科幻小說之父凡爾納和其他頂尖的科學家、藝術家們組成了一個祕密團體，共同打造一個理想計畫&mdash;「明日世界」，傳言中，華特迪士尼也是創辦人之一，在他的遺物中有一個黑盒子，裝著神祕的機關。可是這個計劃卻出了意外，「明日世界」也從此消失..<br />\n<br />\n3 00AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c57e4c37dfd1369eb689cf58f202f1dbf0df40","tid":207137,"uid